# Insider Cluster Watch - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values

# Email Configuration (Required)
GMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=your-16-char-app-password
RECIPIENT_EMAIL=recipient@example.com

# API Keys (Required)
RAPIDAPI_KEY=your-rapidapi-key-here
FMP_API_KEY=your-fmp-api-key-here

# Optional API Keys
CONGRESS_GOV_API_KEY=your-congress-api-key-here

# API Key Setup Instructions:
#
# 1. RAPIDAPI_KEY (Politician Trading Data)
#    - Sign up at https://rapidapi.com/
#    - Subscribe to PoliticianTradeTracker API (100 calls/month free)
#    - Copy your API key from the dashboard
#
# 2. FMP_API_KEY (13F Institutional Holdings)
#    - Sign up at https://financialmodelingprep.com/developer/docs
#    - Free tier: 250 API calls per day
#    - Copy your API key from the dashboard
#
# 3. CONGRESS_GOV_API_KEY (Optional - Automated Politician Status Updates)
#    - Sign up at https://api.congress.gov/sign-up/
#    - Free, unlimited API calls
#    - Copy your API key from the confirmation email
#
# 4. Gmail App Password
#    - Enable 2FA on your Gmail account
#    - Go to https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#    - Generate an app password for "Mail"
#    - Copy the 16-character password (no spaces)
